Object.Field: LKM Oracle to Oracle Pull (DB Link)
SNP_TRT : LKM Oracle to Oracle (DB Link)

COMPONENT NAME: LKM Oracle to Oracle Pull (DB Link) COMPONENT VERSION: 12.1.2.0.0 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.2.0.0 or above
DESCRIPTION:
In the target database, pull data from source over an Oracle database link.
If this property is set to True a temporary view will be created on source database based on the source select statement. The view will be dropped at the end of execution.
Use DRIVING_SITE hint to execute query on source database

If set to True the source SQL query will contain /*+ DRIVING_SITE(<alias>) */ hint. The DRIVING_SITE hint instructs the optimizer to execute the query at a different site than that selected by the database. This hint is useful if you are using distributed query optimization.
Database link name for accessing source database
Enter the name of the database link. If not set a default name will be used.

<?
String dblinkToSrc = "$[dbLinkName]";
if ("".equals(dblinkToSrc)) {
  dblinkToSrc = odiRef.getInfo("SRC_LSCHEMA_NAME");
}
if ("TRUE".equals("$[isConcurrent]")) {
  dblinkToSrc += "%UNIQUE_SESSION_TAG";
}
dblinkToSrc = dblinkToSrc.replaceAll(" ","");
dblinkToSrc = dblinkToSrc.replaceAll("-","");
dblinkToSrc = odiRef.getFormattedName(dblinkToSrc);
?>
drop database link <?=dblinkToSrc ?>
upstreamAST = upstreamASTList.get(0) SqlQuery upstreamQuery = generatorContext.adjustSourceQueryForTarget((SqlQuery) upstreamAST) upstreamQuery.setSuffix("") queryText = upstreamQuery.getText()

<?
String dblinkToSrc = "$[dbLinkName]";
if ("".equals(dblinkToSrc)) {
  dblinkToSrc = odiRef.getInfo("SRC_LSCHEMA_NAME");
}
if ("TRUE".equals("$[isConcurrent]")) {
  dblinkToSrc += "%UNIQUE_SESSION_TAG";
}
dblinkToSrc = dblinkToSrc.replaceAll(" ","");
dblinkToSrc = dblinkToSrc.replaceAll("-","");
dblinkToSrc = odiRef.getFormattedName(dblinkToSrc);
String srcUserName = odiRef.getInfo("SRC_USER_NAME");
String srcServerInstance = odiRef.getInfo("SRC_DSERV_NAME");
String srcSID = "";
if (srcServerInstance != null && srcServerInstance.trim().length() != 0) {
  srcSID = srcServerInstance;
} else {
  String srcJDBCURL = odiRef.getInfo("SRC_JAVA_URL");
  if (srcJDBCURL !=null && srcJDBCURL.trim().length() != 0) {
    srcSID = srcJDBCURL.substring(srcJDBCURL.lastIndexOf("@") + 1);
    srcSID = srcSID.substring(srcSID.lastIndexOf(":") + 1);
    if (srcSID.lastIndexOf("/") >= 0){
      srcSID = srcSID.substring(srcSID.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
    }
  }
}
srcSID = srcSID.trim();
if (srcSID.length() == 0) {
  throw new OdiKMException("Failed calculating source SID.");
}
?>
create database link <?=dblinkToSrc ?> connect to <?=srcUserName ?> identified by <@=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_PASS") @> using '<?=srcSID ?>'
